  "text": "For supplemental reasoning, it is often important to know all the possible ways in which clashes can be generated by rule applications (see Section 5) . In order to keep track of the different orders that have already been followed, extensions of consequence-based algorithms developed for dealing with these problems require the use of an NP oracle [CITATION_1] .",
